      • invoke

        @Nullable
@Nullable java.lang.Object invoke(@Nullable
                                             @Nullable java.lang.Object inst,
                                             java.lang.Object... args)
        Invokes with instance object and given arguments. If this invoker represents a member method of object instance, the instance object must not null. If this invoker represents a constructor or a static method, the instance object may be null.
        Parameters:

        args - given arguments
